  "body": "I think we need to seriously rethink how navigation is done. There's a few different navigation bar styles, some at the top, some at the bottom, and some stacked on top of each other.\r\n\r\nThree navigation bars on the browser make is quite unusable, since the WebView window is so small, even on my large phone.\r\n\r\nHaving navigation more like a traditional web browser would be awesome.\r\n\r\n![Screenshot_20220112-133402_Status](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65834069/149609394-64e3984f-0fe4-40c7-b779-825d0e2b442d.png)\r\n",
