    "body": "> Yes this issue has been an annoyance for quite some time, good news is that the design team will be looking at solutions to fix this issue as part of the Mobile App design refresh work that's just started.  Hope to be able to share, review and discuss this work in roughly 2.5 weeks :-) \n\nPersonally, I don't have a problem with it, but it would make more sense to condense the address bar and nav panel. I'd prefer at the bottom.\n\n\nA bigger issue with the browser, is that it doesn't recognize the device back button. Pressing the back button, instead of naVigating back in the browser, it closes status.",
